title: Importance of the catalyst–water Coulomb interaction for oxygen reduction reaction kinetics
content:
Energy Environ. Sci., 2024, 17,6046-6057
DOI: 10.1039/D4EE01760A, Paper
Teng Liu, Yinghe Zhao, Tianyou Zhai
This work identifies an important new factor affecting oxygen reduction reaction kinetics (i.e., the catalyst–water Coulomb interaction).
